    "title": "Urgent Opening Category Manager at Bombay Shaving Company",
    "description": "Grow your career with Bombay Shaving Company! We are hiring a Category Manager for our Coimbatore team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Bombay Shaving Company:\nBombay Shaving Company is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Manage customer reviews, ratings, and return/refund processes\n• Coordinate with vendors and suppliers for inventory management\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Conduct competitor analysis and market benchmarking\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Google Analytics\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Retention Marketing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bombay Shaving Company!",
